需要空間去讀書 但佢feel唔到樓主你無咩安全感<br />\n兩個同事得閒嘅話 試吓多啲搵佢啦 又或者約埋一齊溫書 但真係要溫書而唔係喺度吹水 如果唔係佢會覺得你阻住佢搏殺"},{"pid":"f1c770fd27230cc0f8d5d558fa52ec6e406b8f1a","tid":2262713,"uid":138276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"Come on James 可否試著成熟一點"},{"pid":"473352fa77f4911025518d8b9fa2d0291dd900d5","tid":2262713,"uid":65858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"HD入U可以話係最辛苦最難行嘅路<br />\n支持佢鼓勵佢會好過要佢陪你玩<br />\n忍耐兩年？"},{"pid":"1ed4cc7d0db418803052ac14fcdae1b6576b52d9","tid":2262713,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"882b494b96b314a8150d8760f3ce9080fd19c397","tid":2262713,"uid":369827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站              <br />\n   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KikUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=70b74e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"ac002a1ee0804a2c1e10eec86d7aa19a929fa255","tid":2262713,"uid":106390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:00:10.000Z","msg":"睇你咁講 肯定冇扑過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83abda0750b6aef506e69e9f60a1d6755da91e3","tid":2262713,"uid":369643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ce71471f0cccbf43a1324ea4c2b2badcb48e349","tid":2262713,"uid":369827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"710702316964675cd8e24698b9b7aa52dcb91c55","tid":2262713,"uid":53694,"like